sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'sidebar-items', templateUrl: './sidebar-items.component.html' }) export class SidebarItemsComponent { GroupList = [ { Link: '', Active: 'active', Name: 'Applications' } ]; MenuList = [ { Link: '/', Active: 'active', Name: 'Users' }, { Link: '/admin/medias', Active: 'active', Name: 'Medias' }, { Link: '/admin/contacts', Active: 'active', Name: 'Contacts' } ]; }
